'''潘露'''（{{bd|1979年||||CatIdx=P潘}}），[[江苏|江苏]][[宝应县|宝应]]人，中国[[持不同政见者|持不同政见者]]，[[苏州中学|苏州中学]]地理教师，曾任校团委书记<ref name=rfa>{{cite news|author=乔龙|title=苏州教师潘露呼吁祭奠林昭诞辰 被以非法集会拘24小时释放|url=http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/ql2-12162013094217.html|accessdate=2014-01-15|newspaper=[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]|date=2013-12-16|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207235105/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/ql2-12162013094217.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2002年7月毕业于[[南京师范大学|南京师范大学]]地理系，同年8月进入江苏省苏州中学，从事高中地理教学工作<ref>{{cite web|title=地理教研组|url=http://www.szzx1000.com/tsdtlview.asp?c=84&id=1465&page=0|publisher=江苏省苏州中学|accessdate=2014-01-15|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054216/http://www.szzx1000.com/tsdtlview.asp?c=84&id=1465&page=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。潘露多次因为呼吁政治改革、参与[[维权运动|维权运动]]、祭奠[[林昭|林昭]]被拘捕<ref name=rfa /><ref>{{cite news|author=海彦|title=网友聚集苏州纪念公民先驱林昭八十冥诞|url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/chinese-activists-celebrate-the-birthday-of-lin-zhao-20121216/1565894.html|accessdate=2014-01-15|newspaper=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|date=2012-12-16|archive-date=2013-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130517203028/http://www.voachinese.com/content/chinese-activists-celebrate-the-birthday-of-lin-zhao-20121216/1565894.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾被[[公安部国内安全保卫局|国保]]送入精神病院[[苏州市广济医院|苏州市广济医院]]<ref>{{cite news|author=乔龙|title=苏州中学前团委书记悼校友林昭 遭警殴及送精神病院后间歇性精神失常|url=http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/ql2-05152013104833.html|accessdate=2014-01-15|newspaper=[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]|date=2013-05-15|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115204041/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/ql2-05152013104833.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

